        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Business Question</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Which pharmaceutical drug category contributes the highest overall sales?</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Insight</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>N02Be is the top-selling drug category with approximately </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>63K</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> units sold, contributing significantly more than any other category. N05B and R03 follow as the next highest contributors, while N05C has the lowest demand. This insight helps identify high-performing drug categories for inventory planning and sales forecasting. </run>
