          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Business Question</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Which day of the week generates the highest pharmaceutical sales?</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Insight</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Saturday records the highest sales (~19.8K), while Thursday has the lowest (~17.2K). Weekend demand is slightly stronger than weekdays, suggesting increased customer purchases before or during weekends. This insight can help optimize staffing and inventory planning.</run>
